1. On me *podseća na* mog dedu. (He reminds me of my grandfather.)
2. Ova melodija me *podseća* na detinjstvo. (This melody reminds me of my childhood.)
3. Njegovo ponašanje *me podseća* na njegovog brata. (His behavior reminds me of his brother.)
4. Taj grad *me podseća* na moju posetu pre 5 godina. (That city reminds me of my visit 5 years ago.)
5. Da li ti se ovo mesto *podseća* na nešto? (Does this place remind you of anything?)
6. Ta pesma *podseća* na srećne dane. (That song reminds me of happy days.)
7. Njihova priča *me podseća* na jednu knjigu koju sam pročitao. (Their story reminds me of a book I read.)
8. Ovaj problem *me podseća* na jedan koji smo imali prošle godine. (This problem reminds me of one we had last year.)
9. Film *podseća* na istinit događaj. (The movie is based on a true story.)
10. Ovaj ukus *me podseća* na moju omiljenu hranu. (This taste reminds me of my favorite food.)